    <!-- NOTE: HOW TO CHANGE THE IMAGES
    step 1: find the image you want to change (sidebar, header, question/answer, character, or playlist)

    step 2: delete everything in between quotation marks after <img src=""/> (DO NOT DELETE THE CLASS NAME)
    
    step 3: go to the image you want to replace it with

    step 4: right-click on it
    
    step 5: there will be a prompt with a few options for you to click on, PLEASE click on the one that says 'copy image url'

    step 6: the url will be copied onto your clipboard, so just paste it in between the quotation marks
    
    -->


